Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.73,0:01:35.65,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Takamatsu{**-kun}, your report, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.65,0:01:36.20,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,At once.{Right.}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.85,0:01:38.70,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,According to the Armory's reports,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.70,0:01:41.70,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,our emergency ammunition stocks will soon be depleted.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.74,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Before conducting our next combat operation, we should be sure to refill.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.74,0:01:47.96,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We've got a new recruit as well,\Nso we'll need new guns too, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.96,0:01:48.71,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.81,0:01:53.96,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Understood! Our next operation will be to drop into the Guild.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.18,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}D-Drop?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.56,0:02:02.56,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Otonashi?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.97,0:02:06.08,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just... not good with heights.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.89,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NWe're not dropping from the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.89,0:02:10.51,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We're descending underground.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.51,0:02:12.15,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, underground, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.32,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, underground?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.32,0:02:15.67,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We call it the Guild.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.67,0:02:17.39,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It's deep underground.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.39,0:02:19.77,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We have allies there who make weapons for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.77,0:02:22.13,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,So, it's there to keep Angel{Tenshi} from finding out?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.13,0:02:23.17,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Correct.{That's right.}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.17,0:02:25.60,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,If the Guild was seized, our source of ordinance would disappear,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.60,0:02:28.08,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,and we'd lose any chance of success along with it.{and our odds of success would go way down.}{fyu: this is probably pushing it, thoughts?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.07,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.07,0:02:32.91,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.91,0:02:34.44,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We're coming tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.44,0:02:35.75,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Deactivate the traps for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.98,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Roger. Tonight, it is. See you then.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.68,0:02:39.49,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.11,0:02:42.30,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We'll take everyone currently present here.{We'll go with everyone here.}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.64,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? But what about Noda{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.72,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,That idiot's probably goofing off somewhere again.{That idiot's probably just doing whatever he wants again.}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.26,0:02:48.37,AngelBeats_Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.19,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.57,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get moving.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.70,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't just stand there. Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.29,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I-In here?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.98,0:03:18.46,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,So this is the entrance, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.38,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we've\Nvisited{gone into} the Guild, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.16,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It sure is dark.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.51,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, someone's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.69,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh... It's just a moron.{Ah, it's just a moron.}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.69,0:03:41.75,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Otonashi, huh? I refuse to accept you yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.75,0:03:44.87,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Why'd he pick {\i1}here{\i0} to lie in wait?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.74,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Noda{**-kun} attaches great significance to situations.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.74,0:03:48.87,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,That's a little cryptic...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.93,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I don't really {\i1}want{\i0} you to accept me, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.93,0:03:54.17,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You scumbag... This won't end like bef—{Bastard... this time won't go the same as the—}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.59,0:04:03.93,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Defensive positions!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.99,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,The traps aren't deactivated?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.80,0:04:07.72,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.72,0:04:08.81,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Exactly what you're seeing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.20,0:04:13.40,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,The road to the Guild is filled with anti-Angel traps.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.40,0:04:16.86,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,And by the looks of it, they're all still armed.{And right now it looks like they're all activated.}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.86,0:04:17.94,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Which means...{And so that means...}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.86,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we forgot to deactivate them?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.74,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,No way. That's like asking to be annihilated.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.02,0:04:25.70,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,That's not it. The Guild must have rearmed the traps themselves.{No. The Guild must have rebooted the traps on their own.}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.32,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.16,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,There's only one possibility.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.08,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Angel{Tenshi} is here!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.50,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,In {\i1}here{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.91,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Just wild heaven.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.91,0:04:33.83,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,How negligent.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.96,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,So wait, these Guild guys are doing this even though they know we're here?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.59,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It seems you still don't understand...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.59,0:04:43.42,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what might happen, we aren't going to die.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.09,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Although, we'll certainly taste the pain of it...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.85,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer to avoid that...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.21,0:04:50.85,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,But if the Guild's location\Nis discovered and overtaken,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.85,0:04:54.06,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,our weapons, ammo, and everything else will cease to function.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.84,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,After that, how would you suggest we fight against Angel{Tenshi}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.84,0:04:58.56,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,The Guild's decision was correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.86,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Are we going to pursue Angel{Tenshi}?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.19,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Even with all the traps armed?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.19,0:05:06.20,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,The traps will handle Angel{Tenshi} somehow... let's retreat!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.61,0:05:09.58,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,The traps will do little more\Nthan slow down her advance.{The traps won't be able to do more than temporarily halt her advance.}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.99,0:05:10.76,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We'll chase her.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.32,0:05:12.33,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Advance!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.14,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,So, uh, what kind of traps\Nare set up here anyway?{So, then... what kind of traps are there?}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.14,0:05:32.22,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,All kinds, my friend. Look forward to 'em.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.31,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Watch out, it's coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.70,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.11,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.53,0:05:47.78,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Fool, we're crazy...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.71,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,In here! Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.52,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,That was Takamatsu{**-kun}'s voice...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.42,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It got him.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.47,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone but Takamatsu{**-kun} appears unhurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.47,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's continue.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.35,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Is it really right of us not to help him?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.64,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like he'll die.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.48,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,He'll make it out on his own, eventually.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.48,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.85,0:06:20.77,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Up you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.77,0:06:22.44,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.44,0:06:23.90,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You saved me back there.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.19,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,No need for thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.90,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, I've grown to like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.90,0:06:28.61,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You coming onto me?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.86,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,No way, man!{Wha— NO!}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.15,0:06:34.79,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Will it open?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.11,0:06:36.75,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.91,0:06:41.69,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I forgot about this one!\NThis trap seals off all of the exits!{Oh no, I forgot! This is the trap that seals all the exits!}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.67,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't forget something that important!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.67,0:06:44.92,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.92,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What's about to come is really dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.92,0:06:48.83,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Avoid it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.22,0:06:48.83,AngelBeats_Overlap,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.57,0:06:52.55,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.85,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What happens if you touch them?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.85,0:07:05.19,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You'll be split in two by the sharpest object imaginable.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.11,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Second wave incoming!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.69,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.69,0:07:08.78,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You evade it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.24,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Third wave incoming!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.37,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What was the third wave, again?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.53,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It's an X pattern!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.12,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,So what do I do with this one?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.37,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Just do {\i1}something{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.58,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Open up already!{Hurry and open up!}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.17,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.87,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You really don't wanna see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.87,0:07:27.67,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.09,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It's open! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.72,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,So the sacrifice this time was Matsushita{**-kun}, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.64,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,With a body like that, it's no surprise.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.73,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,The man needs to go on a diet.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.94,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,He saw something pretty nasty.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.81,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Poor guy, right in front of him.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.15,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you managed to make it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.15,0:07:52.70,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, even when you're chopped up like that, you'll still recover.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.42,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,The trap's firing up!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.42,0:08:06.29,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I forgot about this one! It's a falling ceiling trap!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.75,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I told you not to forget\Nimportant things like that!{I said don't forget important stuff like that!}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.55,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,TK!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.80,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Go now and you'll make it!{If you go now, you can make it!}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.80,0:08:18.31,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on to each other and get out of here!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.31,0:08:18.97,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.97,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.02,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.18,0:08:24.85,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.69,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Even TK sacrificed himself...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.40,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You guys sacrificed him.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.36,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Like I said, he'll be fine eventually.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.82,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat the small stuff.{No problem, no problem.}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.82,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We'll make sure his sacrifice isn't in vain.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.82,0:08:37.66,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.33,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.04,0:08:47.75,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Something's...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.84,0:08:53.47,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I forgot about this one!{Oh no, I forgooooooooooooot!}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.47,0:08:56.08,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,L-Like I told you, don't forget important things like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.59,0:08:57.55,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Too heavy...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.55,0:08:58.80,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I can't hold on...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.97,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Otonashi and I can drop down.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.81,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Hang on! Don't just make these decisions yourself!{Hey! Don't just decide things yourself!}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.86,0:09:08.48,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Losing everyone here would be a terrible idea.{Losing everyone here isn't a good idea.}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.48,0:09:11.25,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You don't need to tell me that!\NHurry up and climb, everyone!{I know that! Hurry up everyone and climb!}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.25,0:09:12.61,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Otonashi, can you make it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.86,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have much choice!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.56,0:09:19.91,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You're quite the sadist.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.03,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Shut it! I'm climbing!{Shut it! I'm going up!}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.50,0:09:28.81,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NDon't stop, just keep climbing!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.59,0:09:31.21,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,But where do I grab on to?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.59,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I really don't care!\NJust grab wherever you want!{Wherever! Grab wherever you want!}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.39,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry up already...{Hurry up...}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.30,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.97,0:09:42.69,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna fall if you grab there.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.69,0:09:43.90,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.93,0:09:49.19,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa, what's this? She smells great...{Whoa. What's with her... she smells so good...}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.19,0:09:49.99,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not good.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.17,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to climb.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.24,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you looking at me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.97,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I can't help it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.97,0:10:00.28,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hurry up and climb up already.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.37,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.47,0:10:07.85,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! You can't grab there!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.46,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.96,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, Hinata was...{Er... um... Hinata was—}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.75,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,He sacrificed himself.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.75,0:10:16.51,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.61,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We're down to four, now.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.26,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Hah. You've got some nerve.{You've got a lot of nerve.}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.26,0:10:24.06,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Being one of the last remaining as the new guy.{The new guy being one of the the few that remain.}{fyu: ##revisit}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.63,0:10:25.60,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.89,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You'll definitely be next.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.91,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,An inundation trap, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.78,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,This guy can't even swim?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.58,0:10:45.29,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,The exit's this way. Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.05,0:11:01.68,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.89,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.56,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri! Over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.73,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Shiina{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.74,0:11:08.69,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.21,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.21,0:11:18.99,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.82,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,The puppy's gonna get swept away!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.58,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Shiina{**-san}! No!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.35,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}I messed up. It was just a toy!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.63,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Even Shiina{**-san} was caught up in one of the traps!{got sacrificed in one of the traps...}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.40,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,That was a trap for Angel{Tenshi}, too?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.40,0:11:43.28,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Wait... she couldn't tell at a glance?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.28,0:11:46.93,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,She has a weakness for cute things.{Cute things are her weak point.}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.93,0:11:50.00,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Wow. That's an unexpectedly {cute}adorable trait.{fyu: not sold, might revert "adorable trait" to just "cute"}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.52,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,But she'll be fine too, won't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.72,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You're the only one left, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.17,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Seems that way...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.20,0:12:11.04,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,If we were a real unit, we'd have been completely wiped out by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.71,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a terrible leader.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.92,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,There wasn't much we could do about it.{There's no helping it, right?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.46,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,These are anti-Angel traps after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.21,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,If they can't even stop us, what good are they?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.68,0:12:23.34,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.18,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Should we take a break?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.18,0:12:31.10,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Sure. We need to dry our clothes out, anyway.{Alright. We need to dry our clothes, anyway.}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.26,0:12:35.65,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed that you're able to lead a group like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.83,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Why were you chosen as the leader?{Why were you selected as the leader?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.83,0:12:39.83,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Because I was the first to resist.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.83,0:12:41.49,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,That's the only reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.49,0:12:42.36,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Against Angel{Tenshi}?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.77,0:12:43.57,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.28,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I had siblings...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.28,0:12:47.99,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.82,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about what you don't have. Memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.82,0:12:54.29,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,From before you came here? When you were alive?{The time when you were alive... before this world?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.00,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.47,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Including me, four siblings.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.00,0:13:02.03,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I was the eldest daughter,\Nand had two younger sisters,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.51,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,and one younger brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.14,0:13:09.22,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,My parents were fairly successful in\Ntheir work lives, so we were quite well-off.{My parent's work was going well, so we were quite well-off.}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.22,0:13:13.14,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We were surrounded by nature,\Nso it was almost like living in a villa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.55,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It was during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.03,0:13:21.35,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,In the afternoon, when my parents were out,\Nsome men I'd never seen before were in the house.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.35,0:13:24.07,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Even though it was the middle of summer,\Nthey were wearing stifling-looking balaclavas.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.65,0:13:28.17,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I knew they'd come to do something bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.62,0:13:33.15,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I was the eldest, so I knew that\NI had to protect my younger siblings.{I was the eldest daughter, so I thought I definitely had to protect my siblings.}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.75,0:13:37.88,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,But hey, there's no way that would happen, right?{But... no way that would happen, right?}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.29,0:13:41.48,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, the guys were after our valuables,{Obviously, the guys were after our valuables...}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.48,0:13:44.25,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,but they couldn't find them.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.25,0:13:48.80,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Because of that, they started indiscriminately destroying windows and televisions out of rage.{So, they started indiscriminately destroying\Nwindowpanes and televisions, and getting angry.}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.62,0:13:55.56,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,After that, they came up with something diabolical to do with us siblings...{And then, they came up with the worst thing to do to us siblings.}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.92,0:13:58.56,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Little girl, you're the eldest, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.56,0:14:02.07,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Your parents must've told you where the valuables are, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.65,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Like, "if there's an earthquake, grab these and run,"
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.65,0:14:09.85,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,or "if robbers come, give them these and ask them to leave."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.93,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your parents must've told you something, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.72,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.71,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.40,0:14:19.25,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, go and look.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.25,0:14:25.33,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,If we don't like what you find, you'll be saying goodbye to these kids, one by one.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.90,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We'll give you ten minutes for each of them.{You've got 10 minutes apiece.}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.90,0:14:30.05,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Use those ten minutes to find\Nsomething worthwhile.{Go and find something good within 10 minutes.}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.08,0:14:34.56,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I started searching the house frantically.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.60,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,My head was pounding like it was about to split.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.60,0:14:39.18,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I was nauseous. I was ready to faint.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.18,0:14:41.52,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,My siblings' lives were on the line.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.67,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I had to find something!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.67,0:14:47.40,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,But I had no idea what sort of valuables\Nthey were looking for.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.76,0:14:52.35,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's time! I have to hurry up and find something!{Ah, it's time. I have to hurry. I have to hurry!}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.29,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll bring the biggest-looking thing here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.04,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Heavy.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.04,0:15:00.50,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this is worth a lot!\NI have to get it downstairs!{If I can just bring this down,\NI'm sure it's worth a lot!}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.95,0:15:19.97,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,By the time the police arrived, thirty minutes had passed.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.76,0:15:23.57,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,The only one alive... was me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.57,0:15:24.79,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,All alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.43,0:15:30.15,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It's not that I care if I'm reincarnated as a water flea, or anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.47,0:15:35.16,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It's just that if God exists, I want to fight him.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.16,0:15:37.69,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I mean... it's just too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.57,0:15:41.12,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,He doesn't intervene when bad things happen...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.99,0:15:46.13,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,That afternoon, I truly thought I was a responsible older sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.13,0:15:49.38,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Everything I wanted to protect was\Ntaken from me in just thirty minutes...{But, everything I wanted to protect was taken from me in 30 minutes.}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.09,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's just ridiculous?{You don't find that unreasonable?}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.09,0:15:55.05,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you find a life like that totally unforgivable?{You don't find a life like that unforgivable?}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.37,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You're strong, Yuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.66,0:16:04.35,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,If I had memories like that,\NI'd only want to sit back and disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.99,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,But you're fighting, Yuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.99,0:16:08.00,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.42,0:16:12.42,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.42,0:16:12.99,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.01,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you die, Yuri?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.22,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...{Ah...}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.22,0:16:19.83,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid. It wasn't suicide or anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.83,0:16:22.08,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Someone who commited suicide wouldn't fight back like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.08,0:16:25.00,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, there are no suicide victims in this world.{And besides, there's no suicides in this world.}{fyu: ##revisit}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.71,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Now let's get going.{Now, let's go.}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.05,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.73,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,This is the Guild?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.84,0:17:02.83,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It's Yurippe!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.83,0:17:03.63,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.63,0:17:04.79,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,She's okay!{She's alright!}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.57,0:17:09.09,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,So these guys make weapons in this place?{These guys make weapons here?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.63,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You managed to make it past all of the traps, Yurippe?{You managed to make your way here\Npast all those traps, Yurippe?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.77,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We should have known you would.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.34,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,More importantly, where's Angel{Tenshi}?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.65,0:17:19.05,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Her advance was halted not long ago,\Nbut it seems that she's begun to move again.{Her advance was halted recently,\Nbut it seems she's begun to move again.}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.22,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,There it is again!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.57,0:17:30.57,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,She's close.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.07,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Yurippe...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.27,0:17:35.32,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We're abandoning this place.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.32,0:17:36.15,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.20,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you serious, Yurippe?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.20,0:17:40.33,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Think about it! Are you fine with not being able to make weapons anymore?{Yeah, you're fine with not being able to make weapons anymore?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.63,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Places and tools aren't important.{What's important isn't places or tools.}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.63,0:17:43.33,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Memories are.{It's memories.}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.71,0:17:45.36,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Have you guys forgotten that?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.36,0:17:46.63,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.63,0:17:48.08,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Yuri?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.43,0:17:51.13,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,In this world, nothing with a soul can be given life.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.59,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Only objects of form alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.98,0:17:57.59,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,As long as you know the composition and structure of the object,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.59,0:17:59.24,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,that's essentially all you need.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.65,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You can even make things out of mud.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.65,0:18:08.48,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,However, we eventually prioritized efficiency,\Nand all we do now is make replicas in this factory.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.98,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Chaa{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.98,0:18:12.06,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This guy's a high-schooler, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.06,0:18:17.36,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,In the past, we used to create objects using just the shape and memory of them, no?{Even though in the past, we used to breath life into objects using only the shape and memory of them, right?}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.41,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's head{go} to the Old Guild.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.97,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It's been lying dormant for quite some time.{It's been left alone for quite some time.}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.24,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing there, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.24,0:18:26.04,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,There's a mountain's worth of earth to make things from over there.{If you're looking to create things from earth, there's a mountain's worth.}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.04,0:18:28.36,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We should be able to get back to the surface from there, too.{as well.}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.36,0:18:29.54,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What about this place?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.71,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We'll blow it up.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.89,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, Angel{Tenshi} could reach{cross over to} the Old Guild from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.36,0:18:35.88,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It's the only place we have left to return to.{It's the only place we have left to go back to.}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.88,0:18:36.92,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.94,0:18:40.14,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,She's right above us!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.49,0:18:45.33,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,The only things you need to bring with you\Nare your memories, and your pride as a craftsman.{All you need to bring with you are your\Nmemories and your pride as a craftsman.}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.81,0:18:46.66,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,That is all.{That's all you need.}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.16,0:18:48.64,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Right guys?{Am I wrong, you guys!?}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.00,0:18:50.90,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!{Right!}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.77,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,All right! Prepare the explosives!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.27,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see some teamwork!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.36,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.36,0:18:59.03,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,There are no traps left. Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.13,0:19:01.17,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri, where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.17,0:19:02.37,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,To buy us time!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.17,0:19:18.88,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you came. Aren't you afraid?{Ah, so you came. Aren't you afraid?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.93,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,There was nothing I could do if I'd stayed down there.{Even if I stayed down there, there's nothing I could do.}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.30,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's here...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.23,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.77,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Guard Skill: Distortion.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.03,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,She's responding too quickly!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.75,0:19:55.67,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Incredible. She can keep up with her in close combat?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.34,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Load shell!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.92,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to fire with her up there?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.42,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.73,0:20:04.76,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.72,0:20:04.76,AngelBeats_Overlap,,0,0,0,,Heave! Heave!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.01,0:20:07.64,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Guard Skill: Delay.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.40,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.08,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Otonashi{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.37,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Get outta the way, you two!{You two, get out of the way!}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.96,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Guys! You get things done when you need to!{You guys, you get things done when you need to!}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.96,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Something like that doesn't look easy to make!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.13,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Otonashi{**-kun}, this way!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.72,0:20:44.26,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.26,0:20:46.18,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,All hands, brace for impact!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.50,0:20:47.51,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.68,0:20:54.35,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.15,0:20:56.60,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,The cannon blew up, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.60,0:21:00.28,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it. I guess you can't make\Nthings you don't understand...{Tch... I guess you can't make something you don't have memories of.}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.44,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't randomly make thigns!{Don't make things you don't know how to make!}{fyu: don't like, feel like it needs rewording, tlc help}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.75,0:21:03.11,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Angel's{Tenshi's} recovering{waking up}!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.11,0:21:03.95,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.95,0:21:05.45,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Do something with these!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.25,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Shell squad, hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.66,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,All members accounted for!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.66,0:21:16.67,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Got it. Time to blow this place to pieces.{Alright. We'll blow the Guild up.}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.67,0:21:17.35,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,You sure?{Ready?}{Okay?}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.35,0:21:17.88,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.29,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Here goes!{Fire in the hole!}{Blow up!}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.13,0:21:41.74,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,How many years has it been?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.74,0:21:43.69,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,This place really is empty...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.57,0:21:45.69,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.69,0:21:48.76,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,If you tear down the walls,\Nyou'll have all the earth you need.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.76,0:21:50.33,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,What a crappy nesting place.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.24,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you to make a new one.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.24,0:21:52.91,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.36,0:21:55.83,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get started, you guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.83,0:21:57.42,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.79,0:22:01.34,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey morons, you awake?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.65,0:22:04.25,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We tore down the Guild, and blew up Angel{Tenshi}.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.25,0:22:07.13,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry to the Old Guild, and let everyone know.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.13,0:22:11.68,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,We'll replenish our arms as fast as we can, before Angel{Tenshi} can recover.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.68,0:22:13.81,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,All members, to the Old Guild.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.81,0:22:16.06,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I repeat: Hurry up, morons.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.47,0:22:19.27,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I saved her without even thinking twice.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.73,0:22:21.44,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.73,0:22:25.32,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,It's just that if God exists, I want to fight him.{flashback (266)}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.03,0:22:28.41,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I mean... it's just too much.{flashback (267)}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.03,0:22:30.66,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}It's too terrible.{lol@this flashback not existing}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.70,0:22:34.95,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You really are amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.49,0:22:37.34,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is why everyone follows you.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.21,0:22:40.88,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You truly are a leader.
Comment: 0,0:24:18.43,0:24:18.43,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,##preview, check against ep3##
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.43,0:24:20.31,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Why's the new song a ballad?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.25,0:24:21.27,AngelBeats_Overlap,,0,0,0,,Please, call me Christ.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.31,0:24:22.07,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,...I couldn't sing the song I wanted to.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.57,0:24:22.07,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Angel's{Tenshi's} residence.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.27,0:24:22.07,AngelBeats_Overlap,,0,0,0,,You guys were really fired up.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.07,0:24:26.15,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,Another one that's great is Alchemy! Alchemy is...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.39,0:24:23.48,AngelBeats_Overlap,,0,0,0,,No memories!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.02,0:24:24.16,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then, what happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.16,0:24:26.98,AngelBeats_Main,,40,0,0,,{\an7}I was just starting to change\Nmy opinion of you guys, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.44,0:24:26.15,AngelBeats_Overlap,,0,40,0,,{\an9}Angel{Tenshi} has appeared.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.44,0:24:26.15,AngelBeats_Overlap,,0,0,0,,The worst case scenario.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.15,0:24:26.98,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,...That's as far as you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.44,0:24:30.70,AngelBeats_Main,,0,0,0,,I said, don't touch that!{...I SAID, DON'T TOUCH THAT!}
